1
00:00:14,963 --> 00:00:16,760
Doctor said that Shen is pregnant?

2
00:00:16,974 --> 00:00:18,600
I'm so thrilled that I'm speechless.

3
00:00:18,808 --> 00:00:19,838
Is Ms. Shen going to be okay?

4
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:21,081
(In unison) Ms. Shen is pregnant.

5
00:00:21,403 --> 00:00:23,720
Why are you still nice to me?

6
00:00:24,128 --> 00:00:26,760
- You know it well that…
- Hold you tongue.

7
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:29,520
You more you acted like nothing happened,

8
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:31,960
the more I felt trapped.

9
00:00:34,206 --> 00:00:36,680
- Don't you want to know who is...
- Shen!

10
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:39,040
I'm not questioning anything.

11
00:00:39,081 --> 00:00:41,040
And this baby is mine.

12
00:00:41,235 --> 00:00:42,236
Who is the father of your baby?

13
00:00:42,408 --> 00:00:44,960
Of course, it is my husband's baby.

14
00:00:45,672 --> 00:00:46,673
Liar!

15
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:48,080
That son of a bitch

16
00:00:48,339 --> 00:00:51,000
has been sterile since he worked in Penang.

17
00:00:51,299 --> 00:00:52,800
How did you know about all of this?

18
00:00:52,931 --> 00:00:54,320
I sent those guys to beat him up.

19
00:00:55,566 --> 00:00:57,680
We need to get rid of the baby,

20
00:00:57,683 --> 00:00:59,680
so it won't be a cause of trouble to my business in the future.

21
00:00:59,758 --> 00:01:01,680
I didn't give you any hemagogue.

22
00:01:02,152 --> 00:01:05,040
Do you think he knows who the father of my child is?

23
00:01:05,083 --> 00:01:06,440
Maybe he knows.

24
00:01:06,627 --> 00:01:09,560
Why do I feel like something just doesn't add up?

25
00:01:09,795 --> 00:01:10,880
Have you seen Tone?

26
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:13,520
I saw him in the gardern with Mr. Perm earlier.

27
00:01:15,827 --> 00:01:17,640
You're my true friend.

28
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,480
When I have problems,

29
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,160
I can always count on you.

30
00:01:23,587 --> 00:01:25,100
If it's not you,

31
00:01:26,211 --> 00:01:28,650
then I don't know whom I will turn to.

32
00:01:29,598 --> 00:01:30,800
With my pleasure, sir.

33
00:01:32,155 --> 00:01:34,040
I will stay here to help taking care of Shen.

34
00:01:35,424 --> 00:01:36,425
After she gives birth,

35
00:01:36,512 --> 00:01:38,600
I can help taking care of the baby.

36
00:01:40,027 --> 00:01:42,520
I promise you that our secret with be

37
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:43,801
safe with me.

38
00:01:45,510 --> 00:01:46,511
I don't think so.

39
00:01:47,712 --> 00:01:49,120
I don't want to trouble you any longer.

40
00:01:54,662 --> 00:01:56,400
You're not gonna wait until Ms. Shen gives birth?

41
00:01:56,992 --> 00:01:58,960
- In case there is an accident like what happened to Ms. Rayrai.
- No need!

42
00:02:01,272 --> 00:02:02,480
Your job here is done.

43
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:05,900
And I believe that from now on

44
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,040
I will take the best care of Shen

45
00:02:07,092 --> 00:02:08,840
and nothing bad will happen for sure.

46
00:02:09,864 --> 00:02:11,280
- But Mr. Perm…
- Go back to Penang already.

47
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,311
What's the matter?

48
00:02:24,968 --> 00:02:26,115
Don't tell me that

49
00:02:26,728 --> 00:02:28,400
you want to stay here

50
00:02:31,416 --> 00:02:33,560
because you fall in love with my wife for real.

51
00:02:36,579 --> 00:02:37,580
No, sir.

52
00:02:39,128 --> 00:02:40,560
I've never loved her.

53
00:02:45,926 --> 00:02:47,520
This is just another job for me.

54
00:03:01,782 --> 00:03:03,000
This is the rest of your payment.

55
00:03:07,704 --> 00:03:09,400
This should cover your sperm fee.

56
00:03:16,702 --> 00:03:17,720
Don't worry

57
00:03:18,542 --> 00:03:19,600
about your baby.

58
00:03:20,504 --> 00:03:23,000
I will take the best care of it as if it is my own baby.

59
00:03:25,232 --> 00:03:26,233
Got it, sir.

60
00:04:00,779 --> 00:04:02,240
I will love you

61
00:04:04,867 --> 00:04:06,240
for as long as you want me to.

62
00:04:26,471 --> 00:04:28,960
I've loved you since the first day that we met.

63
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,040
And I promise you

64
00:04:33,811 --> 00:04:35,760
that I will love you forever.

65
00:04:45,648 --> 00:04:46,649
I love you.

66
00:08:08,926 --> 00:08:09,927
Where are you going?

67
00:08:15,782 --> 00:08:17,560
- You're acting as if you're running away from home.
- Shh!

68
00:08:18,592 --> 00:08:21,120
Rayrai, please. I beg you.

69
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,000
Don't tell anyone about this.

70
00:08:25,968 --> 00:08:27,680
So you are running away from home.

71
00:08:28,528 --> 00:08:29,529
Come here.

72
00:08:32,672 --> 00:08:34,422
What happened? Who hurt you?

73
00:08:35,776 --> 00:08:36,777
Tell me.

74
00:08:36,780 --> 00:08:37,881
Or you want me to shout

75
00:08:37,942 --> 00:08:40,200
that a daughter-in-law is trying to run away from home?

76
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,221
Rayrai,

77
00:08:41,248 --> 00:08:42,249
I beg of you.

78
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:45,720
Think about it, when I am not around,

79
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:47,840
you will be the only daughter-in-law in this house.

80
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:49,400
Aren't you happy about that?

81
00:08:52,904 --> 00:08:53,905
You know what?

82
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:55,101
Since we've been living under the same roof,

83
00:08:55,646 --> 00:08:57,720
this is the first time that I like your word.

84
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,201
Just go.

85
00:09:00,328 --> 00:09:01,720
And don't ever come back here again.

86
00:09:03,331 --> 00:09:04,332
Wait,

87
00:09:05,742 --> 00:09:07,360
Khunying is in the living room at the front.

88
00:09:07,678 --> 00:09:08,960
You need to use the door at the side of this house.

89
00:09:09,288 --> 00:09:10,520
Go around the side of the house.

90
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,521
I will watch the front door for you.

91
00:09:15,654 --> 00:09:16,655
Take it,

92
00:09:17,035 --> 00:09:18,200
for your traveling fee.

93
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,840
And you need to escape as far from here as possible.

94
00:09:22,230 --> 00:09:24,131
Don't ever step foot in this place again.

95
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,520
Thank you, Rayrai.

96
00:09:43,691 --> 00:09:44,840
Little Nualnoi, you should go.

97
00:09:45,446 --> 00:09:46,447
Fly away.

98
00:09:51,787 --> 00:09:55,040
Harder, okay? Use your muscles.

99
00:09:55,726 --> 00:09:56,727
That's right.

100
00:10:04,779 --> 00:10:06,600
What? What is that sound?

101
00:11:05,384 --> 00:11:06,385
Go!

102
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,240
Shen will have dinner at her dad's house,

103
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:22,271
we don't have to wait for her.

104
00:11:22,926 --> 00:11:24,280
She's back already, sir.

105
00:11:24,856 --> 00:11:26,520
She didn't go out to find you?

106
00:11:26,791 --> 00:11:27,792
Find me?

107
00:11:28,635 --> 00:11:30,636
She came back and asked for Tone

108
00:11:30,808 --> 00:11:33,440
so I told her that he was in the garden with you.

109
00:11:33,555 --> 00:11:35,100
Then she walked to the garden right away.

110
00:11:36,163 --> 00:11:37,164
How long was it?

111
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,600
For a while now.

112
00:11:40,678 --> 00:11:41,920
What is going on, Perm?

113
00:11:42,982 --> 00:11:43,983
Perm?

114
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:46,760
What is wrong with this couple?

115
00:11:58,111 --> 00:11:59,112
Shen!

116
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,880
Tone, get the car ready.

117
00:12:38,219 --> 00:12:39,360
Where are you heading to, sir?

118
00:12:39,462 --> 00:12:40,800
- I can drive you.
- No need to.

119
00:12:41,008 --> 00:12:42,009
Go!

120
00:12:52,010 --> 00:12:54,968
Ms. Shen? What happened?

121
00:12:59,118 --> 00:13:00,119
Ms. Shen?

122
00:13:03,774 --> 00:13:05,400
There, there. It's going to be fine.

123
00:13:05,422 --> 00:13:07,080
I am right here, I am here for you.

124
00:13:07,214 --> 00:13:09,840
Cry it out, let it all out.

125
00:13:17,160 --> 00:13:19,120
I want to run away somewhere far away,

126
00:13:20,587 --> 00:13:22,560
to the place where nobody knows me.

127
00:13:24,731 --> 00:13:27,403
I can't trust anyone, Lang.

128
00:13:31,451 --> 00:13:34,160
What is going on? Who hurt you?

129
00:13:36,848 --> 00:13:37,849
My husband

130
00:13:38,715 --> 00:13:41,168
hired Tone to sleep with me

131
00:13:42,326 --> 00:13:43,920
so that I would get pregnant.

132
00:13:45,323 --> 00:13:46,324
What?

133
00:13:46,802 --> 00:13:49,920
When I got pregnant, Tone's duty was done.

134
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,780
And he got paid.

135
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:57,480
They acted as if I am not a human.

136
00:13:58,140 --> 00:14:00,080
Like I am not a human being.

137
00:14:00,424 --> 00:14:02,520
Oh my goodness.

138
00:14:03,179 --> 00:14:04,336
You poor thing.

139
00:14:11,456 --> 00:14:12,920
Why did it turn out this way?

140
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:17,400
I can't live in that house any longer.

141
00:14:23,182 --> 00:14:24,183
Dear,

142
00:14:25,875 --> 00:14:26,876
it's fine.

143
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:30,158
Just come back here.

144
00:14:30,579 --> 00:14:32,320
You still have me.

145
00:14:34,515 --> 00:14:36,720
But you want me to live in the house

146
00:14:37,523 --> 00:14:39,880
with dad who forced me to have an abortion?

147
00:14:41,912 --> 00:14:44,320
He doesn't see me as his daughter either.

148
00:14:45,283 --> 00:14:46,440
I can't

149
00:14:46,851 --> 00:14:48,600
live in this house either.

150
00:14:49,979 --> 00:14:52,160
Where should I go?

151
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,880
What should I do?

152
00:14:55,755 --> 00:14:57,640
Where should I live?

153
00:15:07,035 --> 00:15:08,960
Perm is here to take me back for sure.

154
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:10,600
What should I do?

155
00:15:11,611 --> 00:15:13,080
Lang, what should I do?

156
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,560
What is going on, sir?

157
00:15:24,971 --> 00:15:27,040
Why are you here so late at night?

158
00:15:27,126 --> 00:15:28,160
Is Shen here?

159
00:15:30,006 --> 00:15:31,360
She went here this morning

160
00:15:31,715 --> 00:15:33,200
but she went back in the evening.

161
00:15:33,678 --> 00:15:35,100
Why? She hasn't been home yet?

162
00:15:35,774 --> 00:15:37,840
She was and then she left without a note.

163
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,120
What is going on?

164
00:15:45,782 --> 00:15:47,000
Was Shen here?

165
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:48,800
She wasn't here.

166
00:15:48,938 --> 00:15:51,280
If she was here, she would come to see me first.

167
00:15:51,330 --> 00:15:52,720
Is everything okay?

168
00:15:54,744 --> 00:15:56,400
A little misunderstanding happened

169
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:58,840
so Shen packed up and left the house.

170
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:01,521
That spoiled brat.

171
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:04,480
If I found her, I would flog her real bad.

172
00:16:08,471 --> 00:16:09,800
I think I should go.

173
00:16:10,272 --> 00:16:11,840
Please let me know when you found her.

174
00:16:12,503 --> 00:16:13,504
Sure, I will.

175
00:16:22,344 --> 00:16:23,345
Lang,

176
00:16:23,731 --> 00:16:25,960
tell our guys to help searching for Shen.

177
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:27,561
Yes, sir.

178
00:16:58,280 --> 00:16:59,281
Dear?

179
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,600
You can come out now. They are all gone.

180
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:03,680
Was Perm here?

181
00:17:04,360 --> 00:17:07,200
That's right. Tone was here too.

182
00:17:07,739 --> 00:17:09,520
They both look so worried about you.

183
00:17:09,979 --> 00:17:12,760
Your dad told our guys to look for you.

184
00:17:15,584 --> 00:17:17,040
Nobody really cares about me.

185
00:17:18,544 --> 00:17:21,120
My husband sees me as a baby machine.

186
00:17:22,597 --> 00:17:25,680
Tone sees me as a job that he got paid for.

187
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,080
And my dad?

188
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:31,520
He only cares about losing benefits in his business.

189
00:17:33,403 --> 00:17:35,240
Oh my goodness.

190
00:17:41,683 --> 00:17:42,920
What about this?

191
00:17:43,323 --> 00:17:46,360
You can stay with Pingping, my sister in Suphanburi.

192
00:17:46,912 --> 00:17:48,680
But you need to leave tomorrow.

193
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,920
The first ferry will leave at 7 a.m.

194
00:17:51,296 --> 00:17:52,680
You can stay here tonight.

195
00:17:53,472 --> 00:17:54,473
And..

196
00:17:55,339 --> 00:17:57,080
are you sure that I can stay with her?

197
00:17:57,835 --> 00:17:59,080
Of course, you can.

198
00:17:59,424 --> 00:18:01,160
She knows you

199
00:18:01,398 --> 00:18:03,240
and she adores you so much.

200
00:18:09,579 --> 00:18:11,400
I will start over

201
00:18:12,784 --> 00:18:14,040
with my baby

202
00:18:15,214 --> 00:18:16,840
with the life that I choose.

203
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:20,800
Nobody can control me anymore.

204
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:15,100
I will check outside.

205
00:19:28,603 --> 00:19:29,604
Ms. Shen!

206
00:19:37,427 --> 00:19:38,428
Ms. Shen!

207
00:19:41,864 --> 00:19:42,865
Ms. Shen!

208
00:20:12,723 --> 00:20:14,000
I don't see her outside, sir.

209
00:20:17,646 --> 00:20:18,647
Is this the place?

210
00:20:20,579 --> 00:20:22,120
Where you used to work?

211
00:20:28,083 --> 00:20:29,084
Yes, sir.

212
00:20:31,528 --> 00:20:33,040
Why did your voice sound like that?

213
00:20:40,157 --> 00:20:41,840
Or should I call…

214
00:20:45,841 --> 00:20:48,040
a make love spot for both of you?

215
00:20:51,296 --> 00:20:52,480
But I don't think so.

216
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:57,081
You said that you didn't really fall in love with my wife.

217
00:21:01,515 --> 00:21:03,160
Look at me!

218
00:21:10,320 --> 00:21:12,800
It's the working space, sir.

219
00:21:37,291 --> 00:21:38,292
Mr. Perm!

220
00:21:38,859 --> 00:21:42,120
Calm down, Mr. Perm. Mr. Perm!

221
00:21:43,657 --> 00:21:44,658
You have no idea

222
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:47,400
how I felt when I wanted to do it but I couldn't.

223
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:51,200
She was right there by my side.

224
00:21:52,219 --> 00:21:53,480
She slept right next to me every night

225
00:21:54,272 --> 00:21:55,760
but I couldn't do anything with her.

226
00:21:55,899 --> 00:21:57,440
I wanted to make love to her.

227
00:21:57,500 --> 00:21:59,601
You have no idea how horrible I felt.

228
00:22:00,236 --> 00:22:01,560
You have no idea.

229
00:22:04,683 --> 00:22:06,190
Argh!

230
00:22:06,459 --> 00:22:08,400
- Where are you, bitch?
- Mr. Perm.

231
00:22:08,438 --> 00:22:11,080
- Mr. Perm! Calm down.
- Shen! You bitch!

232
00:22:14,316 --> 00:22:15,317
Mr. Perm!

233
00:22:17,656 --> 00:22:18,760
Please calm down.

234
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,680
I think you should go home

235
00:22:26,190 --> 00:22:27,191
and rest.

236
00:22:28,654 --> 00:22:30,720
I will look for her tonight,

237
00:22:31,806 --> 00:22:32,807
around the city,

238
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:34,401
all night.

239
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:44,401
Shen.

240
00:22:57,582 --> 00:22:58,583
Perm!

241
00:23:00,654 --> 00:23:02,120
How was it? Did you find her?

242
00:23:04,971 --> 00:23:06,480
Oh my goodness.

243
00:23:06,832 --> 00:23:08,760
She is pregnant.

244
00:23:09,046 --> 00:23:10,760
She is out in the middle of the night,

245
00:23:10,780 --> 00:23:12,235
what are you going to do if something happens to her?

246
00:23:13,008 --> 00:23:16,200
Look at you! What kind of a husband you are!

247
00:23:16,475 --> 00:23:18,400
What did you do? Why did she run away?

248
00:23:18,517 --> 00:23:19,960
If people find out about it, it will be embarrassing.

249
00:23:20,731 --> 00:23:21,732
That's right.

250
00:23:22,496 --> 00:23:23,960
You can't even take care of your wife.

251
00:23:24,587 --> 00:23:26,720
I wouldn't let that happen to my wife.

252
00:23:27,595 --> 00:23:29,480
Perhaps the problem is your wife.

253
00:23:29,875 --> 00:23:30,876
She could have gone wild.

254
00:23:31,224 --> 00:23:33,660
- A good woman wouldn't run away…
- ENOUGH!

255
00:23:39,755 --> 00:23:41,000
Isn't it because of you?

256
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:44,600
You're mocking and trying to hurt her when you have your chance.

257
00:23:45,654 --> 00:23:46,920
I don't know what is wrong with your jealousy.

258
00:23:46,950 --> 00:23:48,560
You too, Term!

259
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:52,120
You were so nasty to my wife.

260
00:23:52,141 --> 00:23:54,160
Have you ever thought of how disgusting she felt?

261
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,281
Mom, you too.

262
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:02,761
She is your daughter-in-law

263
00:24:03,774 --> 00:24:05,720
and you should have treated her like your own daughter.

264
00:24:05,775 --> 00:24:08,240
Instead, you scolded her worse than you did with the servants.

265
00:24:09,723 --> 00:24:12,480
It's your fault that she ran away, all of you!

266
00:24:12,700 --> 00:24:14,680
She ran away because of you! All of you!

267
00:25:43,575 --> 00:25:46,160
Ms. Shen, it's time to wake up.

268
00:25:50,120 --> 00:25:52,320
After washing your face, you should have some congee

269
00:25:52,379 --> 00:25:53,380
before you leave.

270
00:26:02,080 --> 00:26:04,000
You should eat more to gain your energy.

271
00:26:04,081 --> 00:26:05,582
It will be a long journey ahead.

272
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:10,041
I also packed hot buns for you to eat along the way.

273
00:26:10,341 --> 00:26:12,642
I put big egg yolks in the middle, the way you like it.

274
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:17,521
Thank you, Lang.

275
00:26:21,280 --> 00:26:22,281
And…

276
00:26:41,520 --> 00:26:43,400
You want me to have this?

277
00:26:44,621 --> 00:26:47,440
You will travel by yourself, you need it to protect you.

278
00:26:56,704 --> 00:26:57,705
Dear,

279
00:27:01,936 --> 00:27:03,500
I raised you

280
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:06,051
with my own hands.

281
00:27:06,984 --> 00:27:09,000
I wouldn't let any insects climb on you or hurt you.

282
00:27:10,099 --> 00:27:13,100
But now I need to let you wander alone.

283
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:15,320
I really want to go with you.

284
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,280
It's okay.

285
00:27:21,484 --> 00:27:23,000
You raised me

286
00:27:23,704 --> 00:27:25,560
to be strong.

287
00:27:27,128 --> 00:27:28,760
I can take care of myself.

288
00:27:32,840 --> 00:27:34,320
Don't you worry about me.

289
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:38,680
I will try to visit you.

290
00:27:39,315 --> 00:27:40,960
Please take good care of yourself.

291
00:27:41,966 --> 00:27:43,200
You too.

292
00:28:26,024 --> 00:28:27,960
Mister? Can you go faster than this?

293
00:28:28,430 --> 00:28:29,480
Yes, ma'am.

294
00:28:29,704 --> 00:28:30,705
Speed up! Come on.

295
00:28:37,937 --> 00:28:40,680
