- Keep going.

300
00:28:57,176 --> 00:28:58,920
Ms. Shen.

301
00:28:59,582 --> 00:29:01,640
Please stop, Ms. Shen.

302
00:29:02,184 --> 00:29:04,185
Ms. Shen, please stop.

303
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:08,280
