because I need your help with something.

350
00:34:02,432 --> 00:34:03,700
What is it, sir? You can tell me.

351
00:34:11,010 --> 00:34:12,248
Can you make a baby for me?

352
00:34:14,701 --> 00:34:16,700
Mr. Perm told me that he needed a baby

353
00:34:17,859 --> 00:34:19,440
but he couldn't make one himself.

354
00:34:21,024 --> 00:34:22,160
And he said that

355
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:24,750
