356
00:34:28,491 --> 00:34:29,492
Tone!

357
00:34:30,160 --> 00:34:32,160
- You're here!
- I'm here, sir.

358
00:34:32,614 --> 00:34:34,040
How are you? Are you tried?

359
00:34:34,115 --> 00:34:35,700
I agreed to do this job

360
00:34:37,084 --> 00:34:39,085
