369
00:35:27,955 --> 00:35:29,600
I want to fly like birds.

370
00:36:03,046 --> 00:36:04,342
I love more and more every day,

371
00:36:07,936 --> 00:36:08,937
and every day.

372
00:36:48,102 --> 00:36:49,840
I've done more than he required me to

373
