390
00:38:10,979 --> 00:38:13,600
Shen hid behind the wall with you earlier, didn't she?

391
00:38:17,136 --> 00:38:18,137
Yes, sir.

392
00:38:22,838 --> 00:38:23,839
Until one day,

393
00:38:25,987 --> 00:38:28,700
I know that I couldn't control my feeling any longer

394
00:38:32,563 --> 00:38:33,700
