427
00:41:05,550 --> 00:41:07,500
The day that we first slept together,

428
00:41:11,067 --> 00:41:13,168
that was when I decided that I wouldn't want to leave you.

429
00:41:30,243 --> 00:41:31,400
What about the death of Shin?

430
00:41:38,928 --> 00:41:40,440
When Shin found out about us,

431
00:41:43,643 --> 00:41:46,200
