435
00:42:12,221 --> 00:42:13,500
Perm killed Shin?

436
00:42:16,088 --> 00:42:17,089
That's right.

437
00:42:41,675 --> 00:42:42,676
Mr. Perm!

438
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:44,800
Was it necessary?

439
00:42:45,760 --> 00:42:46,920
I don't trust him.

440
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:49,960
Or did you prefer to sleep with him every night to keep his mouth shut?

441
00:42:51,854 --> 00:42:53,200
Help me carry him to the car.

442
00:42:54,371 --> 00:42:55,840
You need to bury him tomorrow.

443
00:43:03,102 --> 00:43:04,560
I've never thought that

444
00:43:07,768 --> 00:43:09,840
I would be tangled into this mess.

445
00:43:14,560 --> 00:43:17,000
If I had known, I wouldn't have accepted this job in the first place.

446
00:43:21,190 --> 00:43:22,560
The mess that you talked about

447
00:43:24,536 --> 00:43:26,040
