461
00:44:34,552 --> 00:44:36,100
I warned you about it, didn't I?

462
00:44:36,880 --> 00:44:39,550
Young wife and driver getting too close will lead to a scandal.

463
00:44:40,680 --> 00:44:41,800
I knew it.

464
00:44:45,246 --> 00:44:46,560
I told Tone to search for Shen.

465
00:44:47,640 --> 00:44:49,441
Don't think of anything that disgusting.

466
00:44:50,360 --> 00:44:51,361
Perm,

467
00:44:52,659 --> 00:44:54,100
