483
00:45:55,763 --> 00:45:57,120
You need to say goodbye to him properly.

484
00:46:01,784 --> 00:46:03,480
He is not dying, don't say that.

485
00:46:03,832 --> 00:46:06,100
Aunt Erb, get the doctor. Tell him that this is urgent.

486
00:46:06,187 --> 00:46:07,560
- Yes, sir.
- No need to.

487
00:46:07,650 --> 00:46:08,651
Why's that?

488
00:46:09,515 --> 00:46:11,100
His pulse is so weak.

489
00:46:11,344 --> 00:46:12,920
I think it's time, dear.

490
00:46:13,515 --> 00:46:15,160
We've been fighting for his life for so long.

491
00:46:15,766 --> 00:46:17,700
