- Aunt Erb.

495
00:46:23,069 --> 00:46:24,520
- Get the doctor! Now!
- Yes, sir.

496
00:46:25,739 --> 00:46:27,440
Perm, stop.

497
00:46:28,640 --> 00:46:31,200
You need to stop.

498
00:46:31,680 --> 00:46:33,000
Let him go already.

499
00:46:33,163 --> 00:46:34,880
Let him go peacefully.

500
00:46:35,043 --> 00:46:37,600
Perm, this is Dad's last stage of his life.

501
00:46:38,006 --> 00:46:39,280
Please let him go peacefully.

502
00:46:39,371 --> 00:46:40,760
Shut up if you're not going to help.

503
00:46:40,944 --> 00:46:43,480
Dad can't die! He can't die.

504
00:46:44,336 --> 00:46:46,560
Wake up, Dad! Wake up!

505
00:47:07,384 --> 00:47:08,960
Why did he want a baby so much

506
00:47:09,803 --> 00:47:11,000
