520
00:47:50,739 --> 00:47:52,940
My friend's families sold their vintage belongings and used them for funding.

521
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:54,001
Now they are getting rich.

522
00:47:54,150 --> 00:47:55,840
And we have you, a rich guy who got stuck.

523
00:47:56,251 --> 00:47:58,500
They gave a reason that

524
00:47:59,035 --> 00:48:00,200
after his dad was gone

525
00:48:00,600 --> 00:48:03,000
