526
00:48:05,046 --> 00:48:06,400
A few days after the fight,

527
00:48:07,926 --> 00:48:09,560
Perm happened to hear his dad

528
00:48:11,350 --> 00:48:12,600
changed his will.

529
00:48:13,611 --> 00:48:15,880
After my passing,

530
00:48:16,950 --> 00:48:20,280
