548
00:49:10,203 --> 00:49:11,270
You're right.

549
00:49:13,257 --> 00:49:14,600
What is your suggestion?

550
00:49:16,160 --> 00:49:18,200
You can set up conditions in the will,

551
00:49:18,761 --> 00:49:20,800
that after your passing,

552
00:49:21,208 --> 00:49:23,800
the assets will belong to Mr. Perm and Mr. Term,

553
00:49:24,131 --> 00:49:26,440
when they have children only.

554
00:49:27,432 --> 00:49:28,433
If they don't have any children,

555
00:49:28,787 --> 00:49:30,360
the assets will belong to the state instead.

556
00:49:31,200 --> 00:49:33,600
Good. Write that down.

557
00:49:37,507 --> 00:49:38,957
All of the mess started

558
00:49:40,237 --> 00:49:42,280
from wanting Dad's assets?

559
00:49:47,704 --> 00:49:48,705
That's right, ma'am.

560
00:49:50,200 --> 00:49:51,640
He must be so furious at me

561
00:49:52,696 --> 00:49:54,440
for running away from home like this.

562
00:49:57,790 --> 00:49:58,791
I guess

563
00:50:01,126 --> 00:50:02,600
that he must be furious

564
00:50:04,560 --> 00:50:06,040
that we run away like this.

565
00:50:08,992 --> 00:50:10,160
You're going to run with me?

566
00:50:12,235 --> 00:50:14,760
How could I leave you by yourself?

567
00:50:22,867 --> 00:50:23,960
We will run together.

568
00:50:25,960 --> 00:50:26,961
Just the three of us.

569
00:50:31,120 --> 00:50:32,121
Dad.

570
00:50:34,062 --> 00:50:35,063
Mom.

571
00:50:37,203 --> 00:50:38,204
And the baby.

572
00:50:53,000 --> 00:50:54,001
Ms. Shen,

573
00:50:56,232 --> 00:50:58,560
this whole thing started with the fact that I needed money.

574
00:51:01,134 --> 00:51:03,200
But I don't care about money anymore.

575
00:51:05,595 --> 00:51:07,880
I love you with all my heart.

576
00:51:12,078 --> 00:51:14,880
Mr. Perm's stake of wanting a child is high

577
00:51:18,867 --> 00:51:20,200
but my stake

578
00:51:23,379 --> 00:51:25,600
of asking you to forgive me

579
00:51:27,528 --> 00:51:28,920
is so much higher.

580
00:51:33,934 --> 00:51:34,935
I love you.

581
00:51:41,528 --> 00:51:42,529
What about Perm?

582
00:51:44,387 --> 00:51:46,500
He has done a lot for you.

583
00:52:01,144 --> 00:52:03,432
I've already returned the favor, all of it.

584
00:52:10,483 --> 00:52:11,484
Ms. Shen.

585
00:52:12,782 --> 00:52:14,240
Let's run away to Hat Yai together.

586
00:52:16,296 --> 00:52:17,960
My relatives from my dad's side are there.

587
00:52:19,118 --> 00:52:21,640
He won't find us for sure.

588
00:52:26,126 --> 00:52:27,800
We can start the business there.

589
00:52:29,600 --> 00:52:31,040
I will take care of you

590
00:52:31,339 --> 00:52:32,560
and the baby. You two won't be struggled.

591
00:52:38,960 --> 00:52:40,200
Let's go together.

592
00:53:18,515 --> 00:53:20,680
I didn't know that you love Dad this much.

593
00:53:23,360 --> 00:53:24,361
What is on your mind?

594
00:53:24,963 --> 00:53:25,964
Doctor?

595
00:53:26,531 --> 00:53:27,232
Yeah?

596
00:53:27,262 --> 00:53:28,280
Please let me give you a ride.

597
00:53:35,787 --> 00:53:37,360
Why are they gathering around like that?
